3) Write a program consisting method sum() and demonstrate the concept of method
overloading using this method.

import java.util.Scanner;


public class acad {
public static void main(String[] args){
Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
int a=sc.nextInt();       //Accepting 3 numbers from the user
int b=sc.nextInt();
int c=sc.nextInt();
sum(a,b);                 //method with 2 parameters
sum(a,b,c);               //method with 3 parameters
}
  // method overloading
public static void sum(int a,int b){
